00:00:26.650 --> 00:00:31.369
in Internal Medicine. My experience in the
Navy allowed me to understand what primary

00:00:31.369 --> 00:00:37.120
care has to offer and certainly appreciate
working in a clinical setting and being able

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:39.329
to sit down and talk with patients.

00:00:39.329 --> 00:00:40.400
♪ [music] ♪

