- [Sean] Well, for one, I think that patient
population that we have at the Greenside Clinic

00:00:46.270 --> 00:00:51.540
is very well-rounded. I'm treating a variety
of different ages and age specific conditions

00:00:51.540 --> 00:00:56.969
as well as different ethnicities and people
from different parts of the world, which I

00:00:56.969 --> 00:01:01.989
think is pretty unique. We're very strong,
I think, in sports medicine. Our program has

00:01:01.989 --> 00:01:07.270
had great success in matching residents into
fellowship programs over the course of the

00:01:07.270 --> 00:01:12.060
years. I think a lot of that is due, in large
part, to the opportunities that we have outside

00:01:12.060 --> 00:01:16.810
of the curriculum.
