Dr. [inaudible] to Minetauk High School. That

00:01:24.999 --> 00:01:30.619
way you get to interact with the athletes
at their school, within their sports, and

00:01:30.619 --> 00:01:35.849
you really can get a lot of additional sports
medicine experience outside of what's provided

00:01:35.849 --> 00:01:40.369
within the curriculum originally. The proximity
to the clinic to the hospital is one of the

00:01:40.369 --> 00:01:46.999
undersold benefits of our program. It's very
nice because everyone can go to a new conference

00:01:46.999 --> 00:01:52.329
that we have everyday, because it's just a
walk, a five minute walk away from the clinic

00:01:52.329 --> 00:01:58.340
and so you definitely get a little bit more
camaraderie, being able to see all your residents

00:01:58.340 --> 00:02:01.700
and staff on a regular basis.
