00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:15.780
medicine and you spend the first two years
getting trained doing this and Central Clinic

00:02:15.780 --> 00:02:20.790
is an opportunity to go on your own without
a preceptor there with you, and so you really

00:02:20.790 --> 00:02:24.980
